overview: Cade leads the EnticeLabs sales team. He co-founded Whalehook, a well-known internet marketing education company that educated over a million readers on search engine optimization, and understands how to leverage the power of the internet to assist his Sales Team. Prior to Whalehook, Cade managed sales teams and opened new geographic markets for Prosper, Inc. Cade studied Broadcast Journalism at Brigham Young University.
